{"tid":996730,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最撚憎人得知膠袋要收錢之後果種錯愕樣","createTime":"2019-01-26T13:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T09:43:19.000Z","uid":163024,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0af6552bce6787964289849d15b3d010ed309954","tid":996730,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:59:48.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日見人買嘢俾完錢之後問個收銀要膠袋<br />\n每次個收銀同佢講膠袋要收五毫之後條友都會表示好驚訝<br />\n作出一個「吓，乜膠袋都要收錢嘅咩」嘅表情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">膠袋稅2009年開始徵收，到2019年推咗成十年</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依家都仲係有啲撚樣好似搭時光機從十年前過黎，第一日知膠袋要收錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別喺啲廢中廢老，老奉咁問人攞膠袋<br />\n收多五毫好似攞佢成副身家出黎咁，唔想俾錢叫佢自己帶環保袋又唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 唔撚支持環保，每次開口問人攞膠袋之前就會攞定個五毫出黎"},{"pid":"a04a2050d4db79012166cb91bb4454e60c763b40","tid":996730,"uid":90820,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:02:52.000Z","msg":"日日都有150個新人唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08da366136072696268d398dbbb9102f166944a8","tid":996730,"uid":163024,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a04a2050d4db79012166cb91bb4454e60c763b40","tid":996730,"uid":90820,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:02:52.000Z","msg":"日日都有150個新人唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:03:32.000Z","msg":"見到好多都係香港人黎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f370985780be1ca1df14c0c0a16a6a86dfa8b6e1","tid":996730,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:03:58.000Z","msg":"五亳太少，要收就收五蚊一個"},{"pid":"b398107d6cf8140ad03f72e1c7a16ebe188b0697","tid":996730,"uid":90820,"